Mikel Arteta's side made the request on Friday after losing a host of players to Covid-19, injury, suspension and the African Cup of NationsMartin Odegaard missed Thursday's League Cup semi-final first-leg draw at Liverpool due to Covid while Emile Smith Rowe and Takehiro Tomiyasu had been ruled out through injuryAs if that wasn't enough, Thomas Partey, Mohamed Elneny, Nicolas Pepe and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang are all away at the Africa Cup of Nations